  "texts": [
    "In the first stage, an initial spike pattern with a low or high firing rate is injected into the network.",
    "In the second stage, the model goes through a long delay duration with some noisy spikes.",
    "Last, the model receives another input spike pattern and outputs the result of the XOR problem (the ground truths are denoted as labels) by conducting an XOR operation between the initial and final input spike patterns.",
    "Specifically, the output result considers the firing rates of the input spike patterns at the beginning and the end, behaving like an XOR operation as the right truth table shows.",
    "The network structures can be found in Supplementary Fig."
  ],
